  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Troop Transports are specialized ships that move troops
  between your colonies. They also deploy troops for invasion of enemy
  colonies.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Troop Transports are heavily shielded and armored, but
  carry only light weapons. They usually carry 4-7 troop battalions for mass
  ground invasion and capture of enemy colonies.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Troop Transports are usually part of a full invasion fl=
eet
  that includes other ships to attack enemy defensive installations at targ=
et
  colonies</span>.<span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
